                    <comment id="12382223" author="oglueck" created="Fri, 1 Apr 2005 20:03:36 +0100"  >Not exactly Oleg, I rather thought of &amp;#39;a replay attack&amp;#39;: Capture the protocol&lt;br/&gt;
